    "endUserAgreementTitle": "Terms and Conditions",
    "endUserAgreementContent": "<p><strong>By accepting these terms, the booking guest acknowledges that he/she understands and agrees to the following:</strong></p><h3>An <a href=\"https://fossiltrace.com/denver-golf#irrigation\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Irrigation Renovation Project</strong></a> is scheduled to take place during the 2026 season. By completing this reservation, you understand that this date is subject to course-maintenance impacts, including one hole closed beginning September 10, 2026.</h3><h3><strong>Know Before You Go</strong></h3><p>The course is closed for aeration on April 6-8 and September 8-9. Golfers can expect sandy greens and tees for approximately 10 days following aeration dates.</p><p>Spectators are allowed to join playing guests for an additional fee. If you are booking a tee time, do not include the non-playing rider as part of your reservation.</p><h3><strong>Charges and Payments</strong></h3><p>A credit card on file is required to reserve a tee time. No payment is taken during the reservation. Guests will pay at the golf shop during check-in either via the credit card on file or by paying separately. Rates are for 18 holes only unless otherwise noted. To receive appropriate rate, proof of residency is required at check-in.</p><p>Golfers are responsible for any damages to the golf course, clubhouse, or golf carts which arise from damage outside the normal scope of wear and tear.</p><h3><strong>Cancellations, No-Shows, and Inclement Weather</strong></h3><p>To avoid no-show charges, reduce your number of players / cancel your tee time 20 hours or more in advance through the Reservations section of your online profile. The credit card on file will be automatically charged up to $175 for each no-show player.</p><p>During Early and Late Season, closures and delays due to snow, ice, and frost can be expected. In the event of inclement weather, call the Golf Shop at <strong style=\"color: rgba(0, 102, 204, 1)\">303.277.8750</strong> for further assistance.</p><h4><strong>Fossil Trace Golf Club is a non-smoking facility.</strong></h4>",
